<html xmlns:o="urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office" xmlns:w="urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:word" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/TR/REC-html40">
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8">
<style>
    body { font-family: 'Calibri', sans-serif; }
    table { border-collapse: collapse; width: 100%; margin-bottom: 30px; }
    th, td { border: 1px solid black; padding: 8px; text-align: left; }
    th { background-color: #f2f2f2; }
    h1, h2, h3 { color: #333; }
    .endpoint { background-color: #e6f7ff; font-weight: bold; padding: 5px; }
    .method { font-weight: bold; color: white; padding: 3px 6px; border-radius: 3px; display: inline-block; }
    .get { background-color: #28a745; }
    .post { background-color: #007bff; }
    .put { background-color: #ffc107; color: black; }
    .delete { background-color: #dc3545; }
    .patch { background-color: #17a2b8; }
</style>
</head>
<body>
<h1>FreshBox Backend API Integration Document</h1>
<p>Namaste! Ye document FreshBox backend ki sabhi APIs ki details contain karta hai. Har ek API ka request, response, method aur payload yahan diya gaya hai.</p>

<h2>Authentication APIs</h2>

    <table>
        <tr>
            <th width="20%">Endpoint</th>
            <td class="endpoint">/api/auth/register</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <th>Method</th>
            <td><span class="method post">POST</span></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <th>Description (Details)</th>
            <td>Naya user register karne ke liye.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <th>Request Payload / Body</th>
            <td><pre>{
  'name': 'String (Required)',
  'phone': 'String (Required)',
  'email': 'String (Optional)',
  'password': 'String (Required)',
  'role': 'String (Optional, user/delivery/admin)'
}</pre></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <th>Response Structure</th>
            <td><pre>{
  'success': 'Boolean',
  'message': 'String',
  'token': 'String',
  'user': 'Object'
}</pre></td>
        </tr>
    </table>
    
    <table>
        <tr>
            <th width="20%">Endpoint</th>
            <td class="endpoint">/api/auth/login</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <th>Method</th>
            <td><span class="method post">POST</span></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <th>Description (Details)</th>
            <td>User ko login karne aur token lene ke liye.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <th>Request Payload / Body</th>
            <td><pre>{
  'phone': 'String (Required)',
  'password': 'String (Required)'
}</pre></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <th>Response Structure</th>
            <td><pre>{
  'success': 'Boolean',
  'token': 'String',
  'user': 'Object'
}</pre></td>
        </tr>
    </table>
    
    <table>
        <tr>
            <th width="20%">Endpoint</th>
            <td class="endpoint">/api/auth/me</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <th>Method</th>
            <td><span class="method get">GET</span></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <th>Description (Details)</th>
            <td>Current logged-in user ki details nikalne ke liye.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <th>Request Payload / Body</th>
            <td><pre>None (Header me Authorization token chahiye)</pre></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <th>Response Structure</th>
            <td><pre>{
  'success': 'Boolean',
  'user': 'Object'
}</pre></td>
        </tr>
    </table>
    
    <table>
        <tr>
            <th width="20%">Endpoint</th>
            <td class="endpoint">/api/auth/logout</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <th>Method</th>
            <td><span class="method post">POST</span></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <th>Description (Details)</th>
            <td>User ko logout karne ke liye (cookies clear karta hai).</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <th>Request Payload / Body</th>
            <td><pre>None</pre></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <th>Response Structure</th>
            <td><pre>{
  'success': 'Boolean',
  'message': 'String'
}</pre></td>
        </tr>
    </table>
    <h2>Address APIs</h2>

    <table>
        <tr>
            <th width="20%">Endpoint</th>
            <td class="endpoint">/api/addresses</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <th>Method</th>
            <td><span class="method post">POST</span></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <th>Description (Details)</th>
            <td>User ka naya address add karne ke liye.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <th>Request Payload / Body</th>
            <td><pre>{
  'address_line': 'String (Required)',
  'city': 'String (Required)',
  'pincode': 'String (Required)',
  'landmark': 'String (Optional)',
  'is_default': 'Boolean (Optional)'
}</pre></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <th>Response Structure</th>
            <td><pre>{
  'success': 'Boolean',
  'message': 'String',
  'address': 'Object'
}</pre></td>
        </tr>
    </table>
    
    <table>
        <tr>
            <th width="20%">Endpoint</th>
            <td class="endpoint">/api/addresses</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <th>Method</th>
            <td><span class="method get">GET</span></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <th>Description (Details)</th>
            <td>User ke sabhi addresses dekhne ke liye.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <th>Request Payload / Body</th>
            <td><pre>None</pre></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <th>Response Structure</th>
            <td><pre>{
  'success': 'Boolean',
  'addresses': 'Array of Objects'
}</pre></td>
        </tr>
    </table>
    
    <table>
        <tr>
            <th width="20%">Endpoint</th>
            <td class="endpoint">/api/addresses/:id</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <th>Method</th>
            <td><span class="method put">PUT</span></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <th>Description (Details)</th>
            <td>Existing address ko update karne ke liye.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <th>Request Payload / Body</th>
            <td><pre>{
  'address_line': 'String',
  'city': 'String',
  'pincode': 'String',
  'landmark': 'String',
  'is_default': 'Boolean'
}</pre></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <th>Response Structure</th>
            <td><pre>{
  'success': 'Boolean',
  'message': 'String',
  'address': 'Object'
}</pre></td>
        </tr>
    </table>
    
    <table>
        <tr>
            <th width="20%">Endpoint</th>
            <td class="endpoint">/api/addresses/:id</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <th>Method</th>
            <td><span class="method delete">DELETE</span></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <th>Description (Details)</th>
            <td>Address ko delete karne ke liye.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <th>Request Payload / Body</th>
            <td><pre>None</pre></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <th>Response Structure</th>
            <td><pre>{
  'success': 'Boolean',
  'message': 'String'
}</pre></td>
        </tr>
    </table>
    
    <table>
        <tr>
            <th width="20%">Endpoint</th>
            <td class="endpoint">/api/addresses/:id/default</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <th>Method</th>
            <td><span class="method patch">PATCH</span></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <th>Description (Details)</th>
            <td>Kisi particular address ko default set karne ke liye.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <th>Request Payload / Body</th>
            <td><pre>None</pre></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <th>Response Structure</th>
            <td><pre>{
  'success': 'Boolean',
  'message': 'String',
  'address': 'Object'
}</pre></td>
        </tr>
    </table>
    
    <table>
        <tr>
            <th width="20%">Endpoint</th>
            <td class="endpoint">/api/addresses/:id/location</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <th>Method</th>
            <td><span class="method patch">PATCH</span></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <th>Description (Details)</th>
            <td>Address ka latitude aur longitude update karne ke liye (delivery boy ya admin ke through).</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <th>Request Payload / Body</th>
            <td><pre>{
  'latitude': 'Number (Required)',
  'longitude': 'Number (Required)'
}</pre></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <th>Response Structure</th>
            <td><pre>{
  'success': 'Boolean',
  'message': 'String',
  'address': 'Object'
}</pre></td>
        </tr>
    </table>
    <h2>Category APIs</h2>

    <table>
        <tr>
            <th width="20%">Endpoint</th>
            <td class="endpoint">/api/categories</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <th>Method</th>
            <td><span class="method get">GET</span></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <th>Description (Details)</th>
            <td>Sabhi categories fetch karne ke liye.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <th>Request Payload / Body</th>
            <td><pre>None</pre></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <th>Response Structure</th>
            <td><pre>{
  'success': 'Boolean',
  'data': 'Array of Objects'
}</pre></td>
        </tr>
    </table>
    
    <table>
        <tr>
            <th width="20%">Endpoint</th>
            <td class="endpoint">/api/categories/:id</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <th>Method</th>
            <td><span class="method get">GET</span></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <th>Description (Details)</th>
            <td>Specific category ki details fetch karne ke liye.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <th>Request Payload / Body</th>
            <td><pre>None</pre></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <th>Response Structure</th>
            <td><pre>{
  'success': 'Boolean',
  'data': 'Object'
}</pre></td>
        </tr>
    </table>
    
    <table>
        <tr>
            <th width="20%">Endpoint</th>
            <td class="endpoint">/api/categories</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <th>Method</th>
            <td><span class="method post">POST</span></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <th>Description (Details)</th>
            <td>Nayi category banane ke liye (Sirf Admin).</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <th>Request Payload / Body</th>
            <td><pre>{
  'name': 'String (Required)'
}</pre></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <th>Response Structure</th>
            <td><pre>{
  'success': 'Boolean',
  'message': 'String',
  'data': 'Object'
}</pre></td>
        </tr>
    </table>
    
    <table>
        <tr>
            <th width="20%">Endpoint</th>
            <td class="endpoint">/api/categories/:id</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <th>Method</th>
            <td><span class="method put">PUT</span></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <th>Description (Details)</th>
            <td>Category ka naam update karne ke liye (Sirf Admin).</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <th>Request Payload / Body</th>
            <td><pre>{
  'name': 'String (Required)'
}</pre></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <th>Response Structure</th>
            <td><pre>{
  'success': 'Boolean',
  'message': 'String'
}</pre></td>
        </tr>
    </table>
    
    <table>
        <tr>
            <th width="20%">Endpoint</th>
            <td class="endpoint">/api/categories/:id</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <th>Method</th>
            <td><span class="method delete">DELETE</span></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <th>Description (Details)</th>
            <td>Category ko delete karne ke liye (Sirf Admin).</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <th>Request Payload / Body</th>
            <td><pre>None</pre></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <th>Response Structure</th>
            <td><pre>{
  'success': 'Boolean',
  'message': 'String'
}</pre></td>
        </tr>
    </table>
    <h2>Calculator APIs</h2>

    <table>
        <tr>
            <th width="20%">Endpoint</th>
            <td class="endpoint">/api/calculator/drafts</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <th>Method</th>
            <td><span class="method post">POST</span></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <th>Description (Details)</th>
            <td>Calculator ka draft save karne ke liye (Sirf Admin).</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <th>Request Payload / Body</th>
            <td><pre>{
  'name': 'String (Required)',
  'margin_percent': 'Number',
  'services_per_month': 'Number',
  'num_persons': 'Number',
  'calculated_price': 'Number',
  'max_fixed_count': 'Number',
  'max_seasonal_count': 'Number',
  'items': 'Array of Objects (product_id, qty_gm, is_fixed, is_seasonal)'
}</pre></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <th>Response Structure</th>
            <td><pre>{
  'success': 'Boolean',
  'message': 'String',
  'draft': 'Object'
}</pre></td>
        </tr>
    </table>
    
    <table>
        <tr>
            <th width="20%">Endpoint</th>
            <td class="endpoint">/api/calculator/drafts</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <th>Method</th>
            <td><span class="method get">GET</span></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <th>Description (Details)</th>
            <td>Sabhi calculator drafts nikalne ke liye (Sirf Admin).</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <th>Request Payload / Body</th>
            <td><pre>None</pre></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <th>Response Structure</th>
            <td><pre>{
  'success': 'Boolean',
  'drafts': 'Array of Objects'
}</pre></td>
        </tr>
    </table>
    
    <table>
        <tr>
            <th width="20%">Endpoint</th>
            <td class="endpoint">/api/calculator/drafts/:id</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <th>Method</th>
            <td><span class="method delete">DELETE</span></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <th>Description (Details)</th>
            <td>Draft delete karne ke liye (Sirf Admin).</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <th>Request Payload / Body</th>
            <td><pre>None</pre></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <th>Response Structure</th>
            <td><pre>{
  'success': 'Boolean',
  'message': 'String'
}</pre></td>
        </tr>
    </table>
    <h2>Delivery APIs</h2>

    <table>
        <tr>
            <th width="20%">Endpoint</th>
            <td class="endpoint">/api/delivery/today-deliveries</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <th>Method</th>
            <td><span class="method get">GET</span></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <th>Description (Details)</th>
            <td>Aaj ki deliveries fetch karne ke liye (Sirf Delivery Boy).</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <th>Request Payload / Body</th>
            <td><pre>None</pre></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <th>Response Structure</th>
            <td><pre>{
  'success': 'Boolean',
  'deliveries': 'Array of Objects'
}</pre></td>
        </tr>
    </table>
    
    <table>
        <tr>
            <th width="20%">Endpoint</th>
            <td class="endpoint">/api/delivery/mark-delivered</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <th>Method</th>
            <td><span class="method post">POST</span></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <th>Description (Details)</th>
            <td>Delivery ko mark delivered karne ke liye. Photo ya remark dono me se ek hona chahiye.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <th>Request Payload / Body</th>
            <td><pre>FormData:
  schedule_id: 'Number (Required)'
  photo: 'File (Optional)'
  remark: 'String (Optional)'</pre></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <th>Response Structure</th>
            <td><pre>{
  'success': 'Boolean',
  'message': 'String',
  'new_wallet_balance': 'Number'
}</pre></td>
        </tr>
    </table>
    
    <table>
        <tr>
            <th width="20%">Endpoint</th>
            <td class="endpoint">/api/delivery/return-item</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <th>Method</th>
            <td><span class="method post">POST</span></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <th>Description (Details)</th>
            <td>Item return ki request dalne ke liye (User).</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <th>Request Payload / Body</th>
            <td><pre>FormData:
  schedule_id: 'Number (Required)'
  product_id: 'Number (Required)'
  qty_gm: 'Number (Required)'
  reason: 'String (Required)'
  photo: 'File'</pre></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <th>Response Structure</th>
            <td><pre>{
  'success': 'Boolean',
  'message': 'String',
  'return_id': 'Number'
}</pre></td>
        </tr>
    </table>
    
    <table>
        <tr>
            <th width="20%">Endpoint</th>
            <td class="endpoint">/api/delivery/return-item/:id/review</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <th>Method</th>
            <td><span class="method patch">PATCH</span></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <th>Description (Details)</th>
            <td>Return ko approve ya reject karne ke liye (Admin).</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <th>Request Payload / Body</th>
            <td><pre>{
  'status': 'String (approved/rejected)',
  'refund_amount': 'Number (Optional)'
}</pre></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <th>Response Structure</th>
            <td><pre>{
  'success': 'Boolean',
  'message': 'String'
}</pre></td>
        </tr>
    </table>
    
    <table>
        <tr>
            <th width="20%">Endpoint</th>
            <td class="endpoint">/api/delivery/delivery-history</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <th>Method</th>
            <td><span class="method get">GET</span></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <th>Description (Details)</th>
            <td>User ki previous delivery history dekhne ke liye.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <th>Request Payload / Body</th>
            <td><pre>None</pre></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <th>Response Structure</th>
            <td><pre>{
  'success': 'Boolean',
  'history': 'Array of Objects'
}</pre></td>
        </tr>
    </table>
    
    <table>
        <tr>
            <th width="20%">Endpoint</th>
            <td class="endpoint">/api/delivery/admin/deliveries</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <th>Method</th>
            <td><span class="method get">GET</span></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <th>Description (Details)</th>
            <td>Sabhi completed deliveries ki list dekhne ke liye (Admin).</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <th>Request Payload / Body</th>
            <td><pre>None</pre></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <th>Response Structure</th>
            <td><pre>{
  'success': 'Boolean',
  'deliveries': 'Array of Objects'
}</pre></td>
        </tr>
    </table>
    
    <table>
        <tr>
            <th width="20%">Endpoint</th>
            <td class="endpoint">/api/delivery/admin/returns</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <th>Method</th>
            <td><span class="method get">GET</span></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <th>Description (Details)</th>
            <td>Return requests dekhne ke liye (Admin).</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <th>Request Payload / Body</th>
            <td><pre>None</pre></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <th>Response Structure</th>
            <td><pre>{
  'success': 'Boolean',
  'returns': 'Array of Objects'
}</pre></td>
        </tr>
    </table>
    
    <table>
        <tr>
            <th width="20%">Endpoint</th>
            <td class="endpoint">/api/delivery/admin/demands</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <th>Method</th>
            <td><span class="method get">GET</span></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <th>Description (Details)</th>
            <td>Kal ki delivery ke liye products ki demand (Admin).</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <th>Request Payload / Body</th>
            <td><pre>None</pre></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <th>Response Structure</th>
            <td><pre>{
  'success': 'Boolean',
  'demands': 'Array of Objects'
}</pre></td>
        </tr>
    </table>
    
    <table>
        <tr>
            <th width="20%">Endpoint</th>
            <td class="endpoint">/api/delivery/admin/seasonal-selections</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <th>Method</th>
            <td><span class="method get">GET</span></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <th>Description (Details)</th>
            <td>Aaj/Kal ke seasonal selection dekhne ke liye (Admin).</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <th>Request Payload / Body</th>
            <td><pre>Query Params: date (YYYY-MM-DD)</pre></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <th>Response Structure</th>
            <td><pre>{
  'success': 'Boolean',
  'data': 'Array'
}</pre></td>
        </tr>
    </table>
    <h2>Notification APIs</h2>

    <table>
        <tr>
            <th width="20%">Endpoint</th>
            <td class="endpoint">/api/notifications</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <th>Method</th>
            <td><span class="method get">GET</span></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <th>Description (Details)</th>
            <td>User ki notifications list lane ke liye.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <th>Request Payload / Body</th>
            <td><pre>None</pre></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <th>Response Structure</th>
